snippet: George P. Bush, a nephew of former President George W. Bush, has filed papers indicating that he intends to run for a state position.
abstract: George P Bush, nephew of former Pres George W Bush, files papers indicating that he intends to run for state position in Texas; move is first official step toward public office for Bush, whom many Texas Republicans view as one of their dynamic future stars.
lead_paragraph: George P. Bush, a nephew of former President George W. Bush, has filed papers indicating that he intends to run for a state position.

headline.seo: George P. Bush, Ex-President’s Nephew, May Seek Office in Texas
headline.main: Another Bush May Run for Office in Texas
headline.print_headline: Another Bush May Run for Office in Texas
